7. Bb3 d5 8. dxe5 Be6 {This is the main position of the Open Spanish.} 9. c3 {
This is my recommendation and one of the most popular moves, although White
also has other options like 9.Qe2, 9.Nbd2, or 9.Be3.} Nc5 {Black's main
options are 9... Be7 and 9...Bc5. In this lesson, this rarer move will be
