it's a much better version for White.} Bg4 {The only way for Black to try to
fight for equality.} (10... Be7 $6 11. Nd4 $1 {Black is faced with a very
unpleasant choice.} Qd7 (11... Nxe5 $2 12. f4 Nc4 13. Nc6 {White is winning
