$18 {[%csl Rf7][%cal Ge5e6,Ga2f7]}) 16. Bxg6 hxg6 17. Ba3 Ne6 18. Bxe7 Nxe7 19.
Qb3 $16) 15. Ba3 Nd3 (15... O-O 16. Bxc5 Bxc5 17. Be4 {[%csl Ra8,Rc6]} Qe8 18.
Nb3 $16 {The position is very close to winning for White since Qd5 is coming.
18...Rd8 is the only defense but after 19.Qc2 Bb6 20.Bxh7 Kh8 21.g4, White is
