[%csl Rc6,Rh5][%cal Gd3e4,Gd1c2] Black's pieces are lacking coordination.} O-O
18. Qc2 Bg6 19. Bxg6 hxg6 20. e6 $18) 17. Be4 O-O 18. Bxe7 Nxe7 19. Bxa8 Qxa8
20. c4 $16 {Black has some compensation but White is an exchange up and is
clearly better.}) (13... Bg6 14. Bxg6 hxg6 15. Ng5 {This is a thematic move in
