12... Qd7 $6 13. Qb1 $1 Ne6 14. a4 b4 15. a5 {[%cal Gc2a4,Ga4e8]} Rb8 16. Ba4
$1 {[%cal Ga4d7]} bxc3 17. Qc2 $1 {The pin on the c6-knight is very unpleasant
for Black.} d4 {The only move.} 18. Bxd4 Nexd4 19. Nxd4 Qxd4 20. Bxc6+ Kf8 21.
